#: ../../M/math-out.rst:5
msgid "math-out"
msgstr "math-out"

#: ../../M/math-out.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../M/math-out.rst:9
msgid ""
"[poss. from ‘white-out’ (the blizzard variety)] A paper or presentation so "
"encrusted with mathematical or other formal notation as to be "
"incomprehensible. This may be a device for concealing the fact that it is "
"actually :ref:`content-free`\\. See also :ref:`numbers`\\, :ref:`social-"
"science-number`\\."
msgstr ""
"[おそらく‘white-"
"out’(吹雪の類のもの)から]数学的または他の形式的な記法で覆い尽くされ、理解不能になった論文や発表。これは、それが実際には\\ "
":ref:`content-free`\\ であるという事実を隠す手段かもしれない。\\ :ref:`numbers`\\ 、\\ "
":ref:`social-science-number`\\ も参照。"

#: ../../M/math-out.rst:18
msgid "A  :ref:`math-out` approach to history."
msgstr "歴史への\\ :ref:`math-out`\\ 的アプローチ。"

